-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LINUX SHORTCUTS



double tap [ tab ] to display possible options
double tap [  tab ] after a space to display actual options to use


history               :     shows history of commands
<tab><tab>            :     shows possible options
<tab><tab><space>     :     shows actual options available
!<history line_number>    :     rerun commands from history
<ctrl+r pattern>    :     cycles through history in reverse. ctrl+r to keep cycling



